  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "'Saucer' Stories",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Disk Found Is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Priest Hears a 'Bang,'",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Discovers a Circular",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "Blade With Teeth;",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Other Disks 'Seen'",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Picture on Picture Page",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "The \"what is it?\" which Father",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Joseph Brasky said he found early",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Sunday on the lawn of St. Joseph's",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Catholic church in Grafton may be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "just another gadget to add to Fa-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "ther Brasky's already sizable col-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "lection.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Those who saw it Sunday said",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "\"what is it?\" was a circular saw",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "blade with a few wires attached.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Father Brasky, who said he knew of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "no sawmills in the area, would not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "claim it was a \"flying saucer\" when",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "he called newspapermen to his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "home.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "\"It may or may not be one of those",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "flying disks that have been report-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "ed all over the country,\" he said.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "\"Let's just call it a 'what is it?'\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Meanwhile, in Milwaukee and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "other points in Wisconsin, several",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "persons reported seeing the \"flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "saucers.\" Father Brasky's disk,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "however, was the only case here in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "which the \"landing\" of a \"saucer\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "was reported.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "Hears \"Bang,\" Finds Disk",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Father Brasky gave the follow-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "ing account of how he found the ob-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "ject, a steel plate 19 inches in di-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "ameter, about an eighth of an inch",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "thick and with saw teeth.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "\"I usually get up about 5 a.m. on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "Sundays. I was at the front door",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "of my house, about to take my dog",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "out for a walk, when I heard a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "'bang!' like a big firecracker. I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "stepped outside and found this disk",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "on the church lawn.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "\"Although the grass was still wet",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "from the night rain, the disk was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "too hot to pick up. I noticed the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "glass ball had been knocked off one",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "of the lightning rods on the church,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "so I suppose it struck that in land-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "ing.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "Tries to Call FBI Man",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "Father Brasky said he did not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "bother to show the disk to any of his",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "parishioners Sunday. He tried to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "telephone an FBI agent whom he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "knows, but was unable to reach him",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "Sunday, he added. Asked whether",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "it could have been the work of a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "practical joker, Father Brasky re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "plied: \"Could be. I don't know.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "The disk, apparently of steel, had",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "a one and three-eighth inch hole in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "the center. Through it ran a few",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "wires. To each end of the cluster",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "of wires was attached what looked",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "like a small condenser about three",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "inches long. The condenserlike ob-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "jects were wrapped in black tape",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "which still was sticky. The disk was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "greasy and somewhat dirty.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "Stamped on it was: \"Approved,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "Dunlap.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "Father Brasky declined to part",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "with the disk. He showed a number",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "of items in his trinket collection.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "All of them had something to do",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "with fishing, Father Brasky's favor-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "ite sport. They included his \"bass",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "bottles,\" beer bottles with the head",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "of a fish - and a fish pole from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "Manila which folds up into a cane.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "When opened, it extends to 12 feet.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "\"I use it in reaching folks who",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "can't be touched with a 10 foot pole,\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "Father Brasky quipped.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "Others Report \"Saucers\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "Father Brasky also passed out",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "copies of his recent publication,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "text": "\"Fish Tales.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "\"I'm going to revise this thing,\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "text": "he explained. \"I've got some new",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "text": "and better tales to put in it.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "There were other reports around",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "text": "Milwaukee and Wisconsin of \"fly-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "text": "ing saucers.\" Mrs. Anthony Hoff-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "text": "man, 3410 W. Layton av., said she",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "text": "and her husband saw one at 8:25",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "text": "p.m. Sunday flying toward Billy",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "text": "Mitchell field from the northwest.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "text": "When it neared the field, it veered",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "text": "toward the south and disappeared,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "text": "she said. It was flying high and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 111,
      "text": "appeared illuminated, according to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 112,
      "text": "Mrs. Hoffman.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 113,
      "text": "\"It looked like a small meat plat-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 114,
      "text": "ter,\" Mrs. Hoffman asserted.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 115,
      "text": "Glenn Rowden of Detroit claimed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 116,
      "text": "he saw a \"saucer,\" about 50 inches",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 117,
      "text": "in diameter, over Billy Mitchell field",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 118,
      "text": "at 10:05 p.m. when he alighted from",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 119,
      "text": "an airplane. He said it was in sight",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 120,
      "text": "for 90 seconds.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 121,
      "text": "William Humphrey, who lives",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "text": "with his wife in a quonset hut at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "text": "3148 S. 20th st., telephoned police",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124,
      "text": "at 9 p.m. Sunday that he and Mrs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 125,
      "text": "Humphrey had seen a slightly illu-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 126,
      "text": "minated disk which appeared to fall",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 127,
      "text": "to earth near Pulaski high school.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128,
      "text": "Mrs. Humphrey said Monday that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 129,
      "text": "her husband tried unsuccessfully to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 130,
      "text": "photograph the disk.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 132,
      "text": "Changed Colors, He Says",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 133,
      "text": "Erwin Rottman, 1328 N. 19th st.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 134,
      "text": "claimed he saw three of them flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 135,
      "text": "through the air in a northwesterly",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 136,
      "text": "direction at 6 p.m. Sunday. They",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 137,
      "text": "turned from orange to gold to silver",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 138,
      "text": "before disappearing, he said.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 139,
      "text": "Reports came also from Janes-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 140,
      "text": "ville, where Mr. and Mrs. Alva Sie-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 141,
      "text": "vert and Mr. and Mrs. Howard Roth",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 142,
      "text": "reported seeing a flying disk about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 143,
      "text": "11:35 p.m. Saturday. The Roths",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 144,
      "text": "were leaving the Sievert home when",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 145,
      "text": "Sievert saw it, according to Roth.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 146,
      "text": "It appeared to be several thousand",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 147,
      "text": "feet up and about 10 miles away,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 148,
      "text": "Roth said. He described it as vague-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 149,
      "text": "ly resembling the moon and as hav-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 150,
      "text": "ing a regular motion in a counter-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 151,
      "text": "clockwise, elongated orbit. It ap-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 152,
      "text": "peared to Roth to be moving faster",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 153,
      "text": "than an airplane. He said it was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 154,
      "text": "yellow on its face, but when it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155,
      "text": "turned it looked silver.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 156,
      "text": "Roth said that the four of them",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 157,
      "text": "viewed the disk for 10 minutes.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 158,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 159,
      "text": "Stopped in Sky, Claim",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 160,
      "text": "\"It fluttered around, faded out",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 161,
      "text": "and came back again, and once it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 162,
      "text": "just stopped and hung there for",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 163,
      "text": "about two minutes,\" Roth said. \"The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 164,
      "text": "last time we saw it, it had a very",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 165,
      "text": "Turn to page 3, col. 5",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
